snippet.title: Minecraft x Ice Age DLC - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Travel back to 20,000 B.C. with the new Ice Age DLC! Discover iconic locations and over 30 character skins from the Ice Age movies. Help Scrat find his acorns, and take a ride down the Eviscerator. Top it off with your free Ice Age Character Creator item in the Dressing Room!

https://iceage.disney.com/

https://www.minecraft.net/en-us/marketplace/pdp?id=09e4d8b4-e02f-4c8b-a982-aefc3e393cde
